 ikke s\u00e5 langt fra Ferstad g\u00e5rd."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "nyheter|trondheim|byens gater"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3c7cd12c596dedd2522d2f186d5e9961f352b8194d8eceedf5326c282350f38a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-14T21:19:27.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Byggherren av Ferstad g\u00e5rd i Trondheim ble f\u00f8dt for nesten 250 \u00e5r siden. Han var b\u00e5de jurist og generalmajor."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1098780.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20General-Bangs-1"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/6d1f8f927f31a022efada0d460e380eb6195ce0d.jpg?597e3b02"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "General Bangs veg -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "6d1f8f927f31a022efada0d460e380eb6195ce0d"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "byens gater", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["general", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["gamle oslovei", "bergjegerkorpset", "dannebrogordenen", "broder brodersen lysholm og catharina", "ferstad", "trondheim katedralskole", "h\u00e4rjedalen", "r\u00f8raasiske milit\u00e6re indretning", "bang", "k\u00f8benhavn universitet", "broder brodersen lysholm", "munkvollvegen", "kroghs", "meincke"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "sverige"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["marius frederik bang", "georg frederik von krogh", "sara marie lysholm", "odd hus